{"tid":1668804,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"施丹收最後通牒 今輪歐聯只可一個結果","createTime":"2019-10-22T07:55:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T08:05:52.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fed2f788e0550f564cab5dd38a90fdd38710a9c5","tid":1668804,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:55:17.000Z","msg":"大件事！根據西班牙《世界報》報道，西甲班霸皇家馬德里高層已經向主帥施丹落咗最後通牒，如果聽晚深夜場歐聯作客加拉塔沙雷唔贏，就會炒咗佢，而消息話摩連奴同阿里基都會係候選新帥熱門。<br />\n<br />\n皇馬今季表現反覆，西甲踢9場贏5場，唔算標青，但啱啱就失落咗榜首位置。至於歐聯仲大鑊，踢完分組賽頭兩輪都贏唔到，依家喺A組排包尾添。據知，球會高層本來諗住將原定今星期舉行嘅國家打吡當係施丹生死戰，贏波先有得留低，但由於受到當地政局影響，國家打吡依家改咗期，<br />\n<br />\n「銀河艦隊」高層就決定提前喺今輪歐聯對加拉塔沙雷去決定施丹去留。<br />\n報道仲話，皇馬管理層查實對於施丹不滿唔止係球隊成績差，同時係球隊喺佢帶領下，連氣氛都勁衰，球隊上下都相當洩氣。仲有，唔少球員好似泰拔高圖爾斯、夏薩特同雲尼斯奧斯祖利亞等，喺施丹麾下都係踢唔出水準，無可奈何之下，先有換帥打算喎！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20191022/bkn-20191022011040740-1022_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20191022%2Fbkn-20191022011040740-1022_00882_001.html&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSGWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=2c50e7db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20191022/bkn-20191022011040740-1022_00882_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0f503eb874bf0c87a48847ea3f598482f60a9781","tid":1668804,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media3.giphy.com/media/nU5RoOucaMrPq/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia3.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FnU5RoOucaMrPq%2Fsource.gif&h=3f917f54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDaddy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725fb5343f325727b3159567b637d66ed58af7ec","tid":1668804,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:57:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">快推行動po<br />\n推到有人搞</span></span><br />\n開咗兩個po都仲未上到熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲一齊討論！<br />\n<br />\n[擴大戰線]  [行動] 與其嘈加泰集會 不如唔搞呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1668190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1668190</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4ad84b51c3fd1d7f542e781f0b34e9f256cb7b80","tid":1668804,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:59:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media3.giphy.com/media/mOAHy3gq6ECJy/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia3.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FmOAHy3gq6ECJy%2Fsource.gif&h=bdf8f6df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media3.giphy.com/media/yn3pOI42oCJKo/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia3.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fyn3pOI42oCJKo%2Fgiphy.gif&h=d3706932&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a717fcb1a9c1b6721b21aecf7c6d76a55557095e","tid":1668804,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:04:10.000Z","msg":"佩雷斯型到仆街"},{"pid":"c76497fcbe4de962fcbf5540a7a445776d68d148","tid":1668804,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a717fcb1a9c1b6721b21aecf7c6d76a55557095e","tid":1668804,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:04:10.000Z","msg":"佩雷斯型到仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:05:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DLU7KyN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDLU7KyN.png&h=f4c5c6f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}